@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title Sunray ROS1 Bridge - System Context

actor "Rust Ground Client" as Ground

rectangle "Ground Side" <<Neutral>> {
  component "Rust SDK /\nMission Logic" as RustSdk <<Control>>
}

rectangle "Yunlink Network" <<Control>> {
  component "Session / Authority /\nCommand / CommandResult" as Network <<Control>>
}

rectangle "Air Side" <<Neutral>> {
  component "sunray_yunlink_bridge" as Bridge <<Control>>

  package "Sunray ROS Graph" <<Neutral>> {
    component "px4_state" as Px4Topic <<StatePlane>>
    component "odom_status" as OdomTopic <<StatePlane>>
    component "fsm/state" as FsmTopic <<StatePlane>>
    component "controller_state" as CtrlTopic <<StatePlane>>
    component "uav_control_cmd" as CmdTopic <<Control>>
  }

  package "PX4 / MAVROS" <<StatePlane>> {
    component "Flight Controller\nState Sources" as Px4 <<StatePlane>>
  }
}

Ground --> RustSdk
RustSdk <--> Network : Yunlink wire protocol
Network <--> Bridge : command / state / result envelopes

Px4 --> Px4Topic
Px4 --> OdomTopic
Px4 --> CtrlTopic
Px4 --> FsmTopic

Bridge --> CmdTopic : publish raw control
Px4Topic --> Bridge : subscribe
OdomTopic --> Bridge : subscribe
FsmTopic --> Bridge : subscribe
CtrlTopic --> Bridge : subscribe

note bottom
ROS 只存在于机载端。
bridge 既不侵入 Sunray controller/FSM API，
也不把 ROS 带到地面端。
end note
@enduml
